精确控制您的3D打印机核心，支持Klipper，RRF，Marlin等固件提供卓.message: Precisely control your 3D printer core, supporting Klipper, RRF, Marlin and other firmwares to provide excellent stability and compatibility, ensuring every print is flawless.

作为3D打印机的大脑，上位机提供强大的数据处理能力和控制功能，确保高效高速精准的.message: As the brain of the 3D printer, the host computer provides powerful data processing capabilities and control functions to ensure efficient, high-speed and accurate printing experience.

专为各种打印机型适配的高兼容工具头板，轻松连接CANBus，RS232，USB等.message: Highly compatible tool head board specially adapted for various printer types, easily connect to CANBus, RS232, USB and other communication protocols to achieve diversified printing.

高清触摸屏界面，直观操作，实时监控打印状态，无线多控群控让每个打印机尽在掌控。.message: High-definition touch screen interface, intuitive operation, real-time monitoring of printing status, and wireless multi-control group control put each printer under control.

增强您的3D打印机功能，轻松扩展连接更多传感器和附件，实现无限可能。.message: Enhance your 3D printer’s capabilities and easily expand with more sensors and accessories for endless possibilities.

各种专业模块和驱动器，优化打印机性能，提升打印精度和速度，为您的项目提供最佳支持.message: Various professional modules and drivers optimize printer performance, improve printing accuracy and speed, and provide the best support for your project.
